-- Gold Fields, Impala Platinum Workers Killed in Mine Accidents, Union Says
-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 2010-12-21T13:15:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-21/gold-fields-impala-platinum-workers-killed-in-mine-accidents-union-says.html
A worker was killed in an accident
at Gold Fields Ltd.’s Beatrix mine in South Africa, the National
Union of Mineworkers said.  Another worker was killed in a separate incident at Impala
Platinum Ltd.’s shaft 14, NUM spokesman Shane Choshane said by
mobile phone today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
